		<p>Cummings Creative Group is a marketing services firm with over 2 decades of experience helping clients grow their revenues and profitability by creating and implementing marketing strategies that work.</p>
		<p>We are a team oriented environment and are looking for people who have a passion for continuous learning and love new challenges and experiences. We have been recognized by the Birmingham Business Journal as one of the Best Places to Work in Birmingham, and we offer paid vacation time, health insurance, flexible work hours, bring your dog to work days, and many other incredible benefits. If you are positive, strategic, solutions-oriented, and love the autonomy to make decisions and drive results then this may be a great fit for you!</p>
		<p>We are always looking for new talent. Even if we don’t have any available positions, we welcome you to submit your cover letter, resume and/or portfolio.</p>
