<div class="content">
                                                                       <p><span style="color:#e99127;font-weight:bold;">We are currently hiring for the following position:</span></p>
                                    
                                  <article class="job-single">
                 <h4>Digital Sales Manager</h4>
                 <p><strong>Job Description</strong></p>

<p>CCG is seeking a Digital Sales Manager to identify potential leads and nurture from the prospect phase into clients.  The ideal candidate will have a strong understanding of digital marketing and be capable of illustrating how businesses of all sizes can utilize it to reach their target audience.</p>

<p>Founded in 1991, CCG delivers and executes multi-channel marketing strategies for companies all over the southeast.  Whether it’s creating commercials, digital marketing, offline marketing, or rebranding, CCG has a team focused on results.</p>

<p><strong>Additional Qualifications and Responsibilities Include:</strong>
<ul>
 	<li>Have an entrepreneurial spirit and motivation to be a self-manager.</li>
 	<li>Not being afraid to cold-call.</li>
 	<li>Drive results and meet agreed upon new business goals.</li>
 	<li>Coordinating with our Digital Marketing Director and Sr. Creative Director to create strategy and budget recommendations for proposals.</li>
</ul></p>
<p><strong>Job Requirements</strong>
<ul>
 	<li>Must have a proven track record of success in digital sales.</li>
 	<li>2+ years of work experience in marketing sales, including digital.</li>
 	<li>Experience building and customizing sales material to fit a prospect’s needs.</li>
</ul></p><br/>
		 <a class="careerButton" href="/online-application/?job-position=Digital Sales Manager&department=General">Apply Now</a>
